{
  "____README____": [
    "==============================================================",
    "==============  U S E R   E D I T   A R E A  =================",
    "==============================================================",
    "本配置文件决定了 Kinder Classify 的所有行为。",
    "",
    "【强烈建议】只修改以下两个顶层键，即可一处改全局：",
    "",
    "1) default_path_template（可选）：",
    "   - 给所有类别统一使用的目标落地路径模板。",
    "   - 可用占位：{YYYY} {MM} {YYYYMM} {MM-1}",
    "   - 例：E:/RAY/{YYYY}/{YYYYMM}/财税文件",
    "",
    "2) default_month_prompt（可选，布尔）：",
    "   - true：分类时先询问月份（YYYYMM），回车默认当月；",
    "   - false：不询问；用当前月。",
    "",
    "ps:",
    "- 若个别类别需要不同路径，可在该类别里写 path_template 覆盖默认。",
    "- 若个别类别需要不同月份策略，可在该类别里写 month_prompt 覆盖默认。",
    "- 若既无默认也无类别模板，则使用 out_root/YYYY-MM/dest_subdir/ 的老规则。",
    "==============================================================",
    "==============  U S E R   E D I T   A R E A  =================",
    "=============================================================="
  ],

  "out_root": "E:/RAY/Unclassified",

  "default_path_template": "E:/RAY/{YYYY}/{YYYYMM}/我推天下第一",
  "default_month_prompt": true,

  "items": [
    {
      "key": "【K&P】杂志图",
      "dest_subdir": "K&P/杂志图",
      "rename": "01. {YYYY}{MM-1}_KP杂志图{ext}",
      "present_rule": { "mode": "any" }
    },
    {
      "key": "【K&P】生写",
      "dest_subdir": "K&P/生写",
      "rename": "02. {YYYY}{MM}_KP生写{ext}",
      "present_rule": { "mode": "any" }
    },
    {
      "key": "【Snowman】iwa",
      "dest_subdir": "Snowman/iwa",
      "rename": "03. {YYYY}{MM}_iwa{ext}",
      "present_rule": { "mode": "any" },
      "exts": [".pdf", ".xls", ".xlsx", ".csv"]
    },
    {
      "key": "【Snowman】date",
      "dest_subdir": "Snowman/date",
      "rename": "04. {YYYY}{MM}_date{ext}",
      "present_rule": { "mode": "any" },
      "exts": [".pdf", ".xls", ".xlsx", ".csv"]
    },
    {
      "key": "【Snowman】shoppi",
      "dest_subdir": "Snowman/shoppi",
      "rename": "05. {YYYY}{MM}_shoppi{ext}",
      "present_rule": { "mode": "any" },
      "exts": [".pdf", ".xls", ".xlsx", ".csv"]
    },
    {
      "key": "【Snowman】箱推",
      "dest_subdir": "Snowman/箱推",
      "rename": "06. {YYYY}{MM}_箱推{ext}",
      "present_rule": { "mode": "any" },
      "exts": [".pdf", ".xls", ".xlsx", ".csv"]
    },
    {
      "key": "【向井康二】ICHIBAN",
      "dest_subdir": "向井康二/ICHIBAN",
      "rename": "07. {YYYY}{MM}_KOJI ICHIBAN{ext}",
      "present_rule": { "mode": "any" },
      "exts": [".pdf", ".xls", ".xlsx", ".csv"]
    },
    {
      "key": "【向井康二】KOJI WA",
      "dest_subdir": "向井康二/KOJI WA",
      "rename": "08. {YYYY}{MM}_KOJIWA{ext}",
      "present_rule": { "mode": "any" },
      "exts": [".pdf", ".xls", ".xlsx", ".csv"]
    },
    {
      "key": "【向井康二】真的",
      "dest_subdir": "向井康二/真的",
      "rename": "09. {YYYY}{MM}_向井康二真的{ext}",
      "present_rule": { "mode": "any" },
      "exts": [".pdf", ".xls", ".xlsx", ".csv"]
    },
    {
      "key": "【向井康二】太帅",
      "dest_subdir": "向井康二/太帅",
      "rename": "10. {YYYY}{MM}_太帅_{orig}{ext}",
      "present_rule": { "mode": "any" }
    },
    {
      "key": "【佐久间大介】可爱",
      "dest_subdir": "佐久间大介/可爱",
      "rename": "11. {YYYY}{MM}_佐久间大介可爱{ext}",
      "present_rule": { "mode": "any" },
      "exts": [".pdf", ".xls", ".xlsx", ".csv"]
    },
    {
      "key": "【阿部亮平】",
      "dest_subdir": "阿部亮平",
      "rename": "12. {YYYY}{MM}_阿部亮平{ext}",
      "present_rule": { "mode": "any" },
      "exts": [".pdf", ".xls", ".xlsx", ".csv"]
    }
  ]
}

